<BaseLayout title="About · AI·Verse" description="AI·Verse is a full-spectrum AI navigation site covering curated tools, in-depth news, and investment insights — every dimension of AI in one place." lang="en">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>About</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="prose">
    <p>AI·Verse is a full-spectrum AI navigation site. The name comes from "AI + Universe" — the goal is to cover every dimension of the AI world, not just one slice of it.</p>

    <p>The site runs three tracks:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Tools</strong>: Curated AI tools with tutorials and comparisons, so you can find what actually works without the trial and error.</li>
      <li><strong>News</strong>: Industry updates filtered for signal over noise — only what's worth paying attention to.</li>
      <li><strong>Investment Insights</strong>: For those tracking the AI space as investors — funding rounds, competitive dynamics, and emerging trends.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>If you're here to get more done with AI, start with the tools and tutorials. If you're watching the AI investment landscape, the news and insights sections are for you.</p>

    <p>AI·Verse is maintained by a team of heavy AI tool users. Everything here comes from real hands-on experience — content is updated continuously, and anything that goes stale gets revised.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
